All Implemented Interfaces:
ChoicePoint
public class ConditionalJumpChoicePointDepthFirst
extends ConditionalJumpChoicePoint

A ConditionalJumpChoicePointDepthFirst is a ChoicePoint for the depth first search algorithm. Its keeps information about its parent ChoicePoint, and a trail of changes made in the runtime environment since the last ChoicePoint was generated. It is therefore possible to restore the state of the execution at the time of the generated of each ChoicePoint.

Version:
1.0.0, 2010-03-16
Author:
Tim Majchrzak
